<i>blowing all her money on one night,</i>

36:11.502 --> 36:13.421
<i>and it was profound for me,</i>

36:13.504 --> 36:18.092
<i>'cause, as a refugee, </i>
<i>you're always scrimping and saving and...</i>

36:18.176 --> 36:21.429
