36:48.289 --> 36:52.168
<i>So I carry that </i>
<i>every time I put up a new dish.</i>

36:52.251 --> 36:56.047
I would have that experience again, this,

36:56.130 --> 36:58.382
"It just looks like shit.
I just shouldn't do it."

37:08.017 --> 37:10.019
You want herbs?
Yeah, I got it.

