It's a chunk of brain here, right here.

38:27.888 --> 38:30.558
She's cooking me...
She's cooking me kimchi-jjigae.

38:32.518 --> 38:36.564
I remember, she was standing right here
and I was like, "Ma, what are you doing?"

38:39.233 --> 38:41.110
-Yes.

38:42.194 --> 38:44.447
Because you're the special. Mmm?

38:44.530 --> 38:46.324
Aw...

38:48.993 --> 38:51.203
Crazy woman.
