38:51.287 --> 38:53.080
No, you're the only one crazy.

38:53.164 --> 38:54.623
Two days!

38:56.125 --> 38:58.919
<i>The women in my life </i>
<i>express love through food. </i>

38:59.628 --> 39:03.966
