And I think that maybe one reason
why I'm shying away from

39:40.169 --> 39:42.713
maybe more of
the Euro-centric style of food

39:42.797 --> 39:46.467
is that I associate
a lot of terrible memories with that.

39:46.550 --> 39:48.427
Working in a kitchen, and...

39:48.511 --> 39:49.804
